Description: Cloud-native cryptographic hardware verification platform
 OpenForge EDA is an open-source electronic design automation platform
 focused on cryptographic hardware verification. It provides:
 .
  - Desktop GUI application (Qt/PySide6) with integrated code editor
  - Command-line interface for scripted workflows
  - REST API for CI/CD integration
  - High-performance Rust analysis tools (constant-time verification,
    side-channel analysis, entropy analysis, HDL linting, waveform viewing)
  - DAG-based verification flow engine
  - Docker-based EDA tool orchestration
 .
 This package contains the complete OpenForge EDA toolchain including
 Python packages, Rust binaries, and the desktop application.
